OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with some bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Risk of patchy mist and fog
OL,8,Ffor northern coasts, with cloudier
OL,9,Fconditions spreading south through the
OL,10,Fnight.
